title: Hear No Evil, See No Evil, Speak Some Evil:  Dallas Psychic Fair Round 3
description:
It's the first Sunday of the month which means another exciting trip to the Dallas Psychic Fair! Heather gets her Aura picture taken, has another spot on reading from Sylvia, and is chosen to receive a message in the gallery reading! Plus some of our amazing listeners joined us for the fun!
